["IC"] = "spell_holy_surgeoflight",
["BK"] = 1,
["TX"] = "A tall, proud Sin'dorei. Very stereotypically so, with a long, elegant face, pale blonde hair, and even paler skin. Perhaps he had once been withered, or something else ails him, but that pale skin of his is lighter than the living and healthy have any right to. Whatever the underlying cause, it doesn't seem to impede him. Like most paladins, he is tall and broad, and has his fair share of scars. The most visible are his missing right ear, the long scratch across his nose, and a small, crescent-shaped scar on his neck. Under his clothes are dozens of other nicks and scratches, but there is one prominent scar on his chest. It underlines his pectorals with surgical precision. That, he keeps well hidden.",
},
["PS"] = {
["IC"] = "ability_priest_archangel",
["BK"] = 1,
["TX"] = "To a stranger, Kironas is a stoic but polite man. Cordial. He does not move to insults or foolishness, choosing instead to ignore with grace. He can only be pushed so far, though. While he's not quick to anger, his anger is rather violent. Outbursts oft need to be put down quickly, lest he do something foolish. As one gets to know him, though, they'd find that he a kind and shy individual. Easily flustered under the right circumstances. He is also compassionate, as an aspiring healer, full of respect for all walks of life, including the undead and other beings of taboo nature.",
},
