["BK"] = 1,
["TX"] = "Originally from Silvermoon City, Kironas has traveled far in his pursuits. He could be known for his time among the courts in Silvermoon, the eldest son of a minor noble, or his assitance on the Broken Isles. It seems he's labeled a runaway, now, though, and anyone who knows him from Silvermoon would be met with suspicion. ",
