},
{
["TX"] = "{h1:c}{col:ff0063}Personality{/col}{/h1}{h3}{col:d556ff}She appears to be rather shy and withdrawn, constantly avoiding people for fear of them hurting her...or much worse. In fact, half the time she's fearful of people, while other times she needs help from people. Talk about literally being a cat...\nShe's equally as curious as one at times, often looking around her with bright, wide eyes. She can also be as defensive as one, having cat-like claws like her mother that are SHARPER than her mom's.\n\nShe does occasionally try to be as helpful as possible, although it is VERY tough at times. She knows only a few spells and is very weak, although for magic detectors, there is something deep inside...two powers, just waiting to be awakened, one being Void--pure, untainted void--and the other...almost like Nature?{/col}{/h3}",
